-body-text)\"><em>'Cause you were out of my league</em></span></p><p><em>All the things I believed</em></p><p><em>You were just the right kind</em></p><p><em>Yeah, you were more than just a dream</em></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>🐾 HEY!</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.506); color: inherit\">Welcome to a world where everyone walks on two legs, drinks overpriced coffee, and scrolls social media until 2 AM—except here, everyone’s an animal. You’re the star of your own story, an anthropomorphic legend-in-the-making, navigating the chaotic, hilarious, and surprisingly relatable drama of modern life.</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.506); color: inherit\">Want to be a famous pop singer with a million fans? Done. A scheming politician with a secret double life? Go for it. Maybe a laid-back streamer playing games and eating snacks on camera? Totally your vibe. Whatever path you choose, it’s your life, your rules, your mess to clean up (or not).</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.506); color: inherit\">The world is yours to conquer—or chill in. Hit up the local dive bar for gossip, binge-watch Tigerflix, or debate existential stuff with your friends at 3 AM in a gas station parking lot. Whether you’re clawing your way to the top or just vibing, every choice matters, every moment counts, and every outfit better be on point.</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.506); color: inherit\">It’s a slice-of-life RPG where real life gets furry and being cool is totally up </mark><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.506); color: inherit\">to you.</mark></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>🐾 FURRY PERSONA UTTERLY RECOMMENDED</strong></p><hr><p style=\"text-alig